## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **abacavir HLA-B*5701 2008 FDA mandatory** = first PGx mandatory pretest. PREDICT-1 trial (Mallal 2008) → 100% negative predictive value. quantum-VQE 의 HLA-peptide binding selectivity 가 hxq-pgx-hla-001 candidate (HLA-B*5701-non-cross-reactive analog) motivation.
2. **CYP2D6 codeine UM post-tonsillectomy fatality (Kelly 2012)** = small-children morphine OD. 2013 FDA codeine post-tonsillectomy contra-indication. quantum-VQE 의 CYP2D6-isoform-balanced 신규 opioid 가 hxq-pgx-cyp2d6-001 motivation.
3. **DPYD EU 2020 mandatory pretest** = 5-FU / capecitabine 5% 환자 fatal toxicity. US FDA 는 actionable label 만, mandatory 아님 (regional regulatory diff). quantum-VQE 의 DPYD-variant-aware 5-FU analog 가 의의.
4. **clopidogrel CYP2C19 PM stent thrombosis (POPular Genetics 2019)** = 표준치료 vs PGx-guided 우수성 RCT. ticagrelor / prasugrel 대안. quantum-VQE 의 CYP2C19-independent P2Y12 antagonist 가 hxq-pgx-p2y12-001 motivation.
5. **TPMT *3A *3C myelosuppression** = azathioprine 1:300 homozygous 환자 fatal. dose 1/10 또는 NUDT15 추가 검사 (Asian). quantum-VQE 의 TPMT-independent purine 유사체 가 long-term goal.
6. **carbamazepine HLA-B*1502 SJS/TEN Asian** = 2007 Taiwan 의무 → 2008 US FDA. quantum-VQE 의 lower-immunogenicity carbamazepine analog 가 hxq-pgx-cbz-001 motivation.
7. **G6PD def primaquine/dapsone/rasburicase hemolysis** = sub-Saharan + Mediterranean 50%+ G6PD def 일부 community. quantum-VQE 의 G6PD-independent 항말라리아 / 항한센병 path 가 의의.
8. **VKORC1 + CYP2C9 warfarin dual + 임상 algorithm (IWPC 2009)** = PGx-guided 우수성 입증. DOAC era → warfarin demand 감소 (cross-cardio). quantum-VQE 의 VKORC1-non-dependent 항응고제 = DOAC 와 동등 path.
9. **precision oncology black-box-mandatory genes (EGFR / KRAS / ALK / BRAF / RET / NTRK / HER2)** = cancer roadmap 와 overlap. 본 entry 는 PGx-axis 정렬 cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, PGx 임상 의미 한정.

